    "<div>\n<i class=\"NoteType\">\nPerson Note\n</i>\n<div class=\"grampsstylednote\">\n<p>\nIn York County, SC for 1800 census.<br />\n1800  census: 1 male 26-45, 1 fem 0-10, 2 fem 16-26, hence Jorden was <br />\nprobably about 26,<br />\nwife about 18, probably married about one year, fem. child Passey.<br />\nIn Haywood County, NC for 1820 census.<br />\nIn Cocke County, TN for 1830 census:  011100001-0000001; Code: <br />\n5-10-15-20-30-40-50-60-70.<br />\nOn 1836 Cocke County tax lists along with Collins &amp; Pleasant Williams.<br />\nIn 1839 tax list Cocke County District 10.<br />\nIn Sevier County, TN for 1840 census.\n</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
