    "<div>\n<i class=\"NoteType\">\nPerson Note\n</i>\n<div class=\"grampsstylednote\">\n<p>\nThere is another Joanna Davenport in theprevious generation.  She was <br />\nmarried to Capt. John Alexander.  Their children were Ashbury, Charles, <br />\nIsaac, and Jesse. Ashbury, Charles, and Isaac moved to indiana in 1811.   <br />\nJesse moved in 1824.  Sometime later, John died and Joanna moved to <br />\nIndiana to be near her sons.  She died in 1835, and had a will that was <br />\nprobated.  [Washington County Genealogical Society Journal, December 1999]\n</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
