    "<div>\n<i class=\"NoteType\">\nPerson Note\n</i>\n<div class=\"grampsstylednote\">\n<p>\nThere is a William Henderson listed on the 1755 Orange County, NC tax <br />\nlist.  His entry indicates only one taxable white person, meaning that he <br />\nprobably was not yet married.  This would suggest that he was about 20 <br />\nyears of age, making his birth date around 1735.  This ties exceedingly <br />\nwell with our William Henderson, with an estimated birth date of 1736.  <br />\nMore proof is needed.\n</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
